			<div class="name">Hack the Beanpot</div>

			<p>A Bitcoin accepting Keurig built at <a href="https://twitter.com/HackBeanpot">HackBeanpot</a>. We tore apart a Keurig, put an Arduino Uno in it with a wifi sheild, an IR sensor and some LEDs. We put it back together nicely and added a Bitpay integration. It now makes you a cup of coffee when you pay it in Bitcoin and place your mug in it.</p>

